83	 * @param {Tensor} outputs.logits The logits
84	 * @param {Tensor} outputs.pred_boxes The predicted boxes.
85	 * @param {number} [threshold=0.5] The threshold to use for the scores.
86	 * @param {[number, number][]} [target_sizes=null] The sizes of the original images.
87	 * @param {boolean} [is_zero_shot=false] Whether zero-shot object detection was performed.
88	 * @return {Object[]} An array of objects containing the post-processed outputs.
